Log analysis and search

Usage: do-memory-cli logs <COMMAND>

Commands:
  analyze  Analyze episode logs for patterns and insights
  search   Search logs with flexible queries
  export   Export logs for external analysis
  stats    Show log statistics
  help     Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help  Print help
